Tornado Rod:
    - Shape layers of EVA foam (cut slot for switch)
    - Glue layers
    - Spray plastic on EVA foam
>   - Wait for plastic to dry
    - Paint brown
>   - Wait for paint to dry
    - Paint dark green
>   - Wait for paint to dry
    - Paint light green
>   - Wait for paint to dry
    - Cut rubber foam into fan section
